User -> App: Enters name, email, password  
App -> App: Validates input fields  
User -> App: Clicks "Create Account"  
App -> DB: Store user profile  
App -> User: Send confirmation  
App -> User: Show success dashboard  

User -> App: Clicks "Invite Friend"  
App -> App: Generate invite link  
User -> Friend: Shares link  
Friend -> App: Opens link  
App -> App: Validate & connect users  
App -> Users: Update friend list  

User -> App: Clicks "Create Group Chat"  
App -> App: Show setup screen  
User -> App: Enters group name, selects friends  
App -> App: Validate and create group  
App -> Friends: Send notifications  
App -> User: Show chat interface  

User -> App: Clicks "Suggested Exercises"  
App -> DB: Fetch recommended workouts  
App -> User: Display exercise list  
User -> App: Clicks on exercise  
App -> DB: Fetch exercise details  
App -> User: Show details and reviews  

User -> App: Clicks "Rate this Exercise"  
App -> App: Show review input form  
User -> App: Enters rating and feedback  
App -> DB: Store review  
App -> User: Confirm submission  

User -> App: Opens "Set Goal"  
App -> App: Display goal options  
User -> App: Enters goal details  
App -> DB: Save goal data  
User -> App: Logs progress  
App -> App: Update progress and check goal status  
App -> User: Notify if goal is reached  
